Your Ultimate Keys Escape
Since 1903, Gilbert’s Resort & Marina has been a cherished Florida Keys destination
. Once a simple fishing camp and bait shop, it has evolved into a vibrant waterfront retreat where breathtaking views, tropical charm, and laid-back vibes create the perfect setting for unforgettable moments.
The Beach
Soft white sands, crystal-clear waters, and swaying palms set the scene for ultimate relaxation.
Lounge under the sun, take a refreshing dip, or book a private cabana for a VIP experience. As evening falls, watch the sky transform into a breathtaking sunset—nature’s perfect backdrop.
Book Now >
Dining Delights
From fresh seafood to tropical island-inspired dishes, dining at Gilbert’s is a treat for the senses.
Enjoy waterfront dining with ocean breezes and spectacular sunset views—every meal feels like a special occasion.
Learn More >
The Tiki Bar
Step into the heart of the action at the largest Tiki Bar in the Keys.
Enjoy handcrafted cocktails—including our world-famous Piña Colada—while live music fills the air. With waterfront views, an energetic atmosphere, and a menu packed with fresh flavors, every visit is an experience to remember.
Learn More >
Accommodations
Our modern, beach-chic rooms and suites offer stunning waterfront views and are just steps away from the pool, beach, and Tiki Bar.
Whether you're here for a weekend escape or an extended stay, comfort and relaxation are always guaranteed.
Book Now >
Poolside
Surround yourself with lush tropical landscaping as you unwind by our resort-style pool.
Whether you’re cooling off with a swim or sipping a poolside cocktail, it’s the perfect place to slow down and enjoy the moment.
Learn More >
Events & Entertainment
At Gilbert’s Resort & Marina, every night brings something special.
From live music performances to private celebrations, our resort is the perfect setting for making lasting memories. Dance under the stars, toast to the good times, and let the vibrant energy of the Keys carry you away.
View Calendar >
The Marina
For water lovers, our full-service marina is the gateway to adventure.
Dock for a day, a week, or longer, and enjoy easy access to boating, fishing, and watersports. Watch the boats cruise by or set sail into the horizon—Gilbert's is the perfect starting point for your nautical journey.
Learn More >
Sunsets & Scenic Views
No visit to Gilbert’s is complete without witnessing one of our legendary sunsets.
As the sky transforms into brilliant hues, the calm waters reflect the beauty of the Keys. It’s the perfect way to end the day—and a reminder that at Gilbert’s, every sunset is an invitation to return.
Photo Gallery >
Adventure Awaits
At Gilbert’s, adventure is always within reach.
Feel the thrill of the open water on a jet ski, paddle through scenic waters on a kayak or paddleboard, or set out on a boat rental to discover hidden gems. Whether you're joining a fishing charter, snorkeling the reefs, or taking a sunset cruise, the Florida Keys’ beauty is yours to explore.
Learn More >
Experience
With a rich history and a timeless Keys charm, Gilbert’s Resort & Marina continues to be a beloved destination where past and present meet in perfect harmony.
From our private beach and Tiki Bar to our full-service marina and boutique accommodations, every corner of our resort is designed to inspire relaxation and adventure.
Breathtaking views. Unforgettable experiences. Your perfect Keys escape starts here.
Book Now >

Meet The  Team—
The Heart Of Gilbert’s Resort
From the friendly faces behind the Tiki Bar to the dedicated staff ensuring every detail of your stay is perfect, our team brings authentic Keys charm, warm hospitality, and a passion for creating unforgettable experiences.
Why Work at Gilbert’s Resort?
Each team member is dedicated to providing exceptional service with a personal touch.
Whether it’s crafting your favorite cocktail, preparing fresh seafood dishes, or guiding you through watersport adventures, we’re here to make every guest feel welcomed and cared for.
Meet Our Key Players
Management Team
– Experienced leaders ensuring seamless service and unforgettable stays.
Tiki Bar Crew
– Masters of mixology and the heart of our island vibes, keeping the drinks flowing.
Culinary Experts
– Crafting fresh, locally inspired dishes that capture the flavors of the Keys.
Guest Services & Housekeeping
– Focused on comfort, cleanliness, and making your stay stress-free.
Marina & Watersports Team
– Experts in all things boating and adventure, ensuring a safe and fun experience on the water
Hear from the Team
“What makes Gilbert’s special isn’t just the views or the drinks—it’s the people who come here and the memories we help create.”

Celebrate at Gilbert’s – A Venue Like No Other
Host your dream event at Gilbert’s Resort & Marina, where stunning waterfront views, laid-back island vibes, and impeccable service come together for an unforgettable experience.
Whether it’s a wedding, private event or corporate meeting, our tropical paradise is the perfect setting.
Weddings – Say "I Do" in the Keys
Tie the knot with breathtaking views of Florida Bay as your backdrop. Our scenic waterfront and charming event spaces create the perfect atmosphere for an intimate ceremony or grand celebration.
Wedding Venue Options
OUTDOOR CEREMONY
At Gilbert’s Resort & Marina, we offer stunning outdoor ceremony locations, each providing breathtaking waterfront views and a tropical ambiance that perfectly captures the beauty of the Florida Keys.
BEACHFRONT CEREMONY
Exchange vows with your toes in the sand and the tranquil waters of the bay as your backdrop. Our private beach creates a romantic setting with swaying palm trees, warm ocean breezes, and a golden sunset that turns your special moment into an unforgettable experience.
DOCKSIDE CEREMONY
Say “I do” on our picturesque dock, surrounded by the gentle waves of the bay and stunning panoramic views. This intimate location offers a unique nautical charm, perfect for couples looking for a waterfront wedding with a touch of adventure.
TIKI PAVILION - COVERED OUTDOOR OPTION
For a beautiful yet sheltered option, our Tiki Pavilion provides a covered ceremony space with an open-air feel. Set beneath our iconic thatched roof, this space offers shade, comfort, and scenic water views while ensuring your celebration stays magical in any weather.

LGBTQ+ inclusive – Love is love at Gilbert’s!
Corporate Events – Work, Play & Unwind
Ditch the boardroom and bring your team to paradise! Gilbert’s offers flexible meeting spaces, waterfront dining, and team-building activities like sunset cruises and watersports—the perfect mix of productivity and relaxation.
Meetings & Banquets – Gather in Style
From corporate banquets to casual get-togethers, we offer customizable spaces and menus to match your event. Whether you’re planning a business retreat, a milestone celebration, or a family reunion, we’ll handle the details so you can enjoy the moment.
Special Events – Celebrate Life’s Best Moments
Birthdays, anniversaries, graduations—whatever the occasion, Gilbert’s Resort is the ultimate party destination. With live music, fantastic food, and unbeatable waterfront views, your event will be one to remember.
